snippet.title: Croakwood - Official Reveal Trailer | Future of Play 2024
snippet.description: Croakwood is a creative, relaxed town building simulation game about frogs and nature! Design and create structures, plan and decorate towns, and explore an ancient forest to guide the growth of a charming community of tiny amphibians as they settle into their new life in the lush and wild woods.
